16d0db0250d818d3ca4714c56fac68cbad655c6a.query:
SELECT TRUE member
            FROM lobby l
                     JOIN lobby_member lm on l.id = lm.lobby_id
                     JOIN "user" u on u.id = lm.user_id
            WHERE l.public_id = $1
              AND u.public_id = $2;

17a5ef1e426215396af7ad9dc08945733f360a1f.query:
INSERT INTO lobby_member (lobby_id, user_id, host)
            VALUES ((SELECT id FROM lobby WHERE public_id = $1),
                    (SELECT id FROM "user" WHERE public_id = $2),
                    $3)
            ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;

8e1aa72d21270b68b564bffd2c2d905087655193.query:
UPDATE lobby
            SET name = $2
            WHERE public_id = $1

a32bef703e476092edf6ecfdb37303878faa7f56.query:
SELECT lm.id, u.public_id, u.name
            FROM lobby l
                     JOIN lobby_member lm on l.id = lm.lobby_id
                     JOIN "user" u on u.id = lm.user_id
            WHERE l.public_id = $3
              AND lm.id > $1
            ORDER BY lm.id
            LIMIT $2;

ae6dcd2c11d602c70813eb2cde6df8248e61ca1f.query:
INSERT INTO lobby (public_id, name)
            VALUES ($1, $2)
            ON CONFLICT (public_id) DO UPDATE
                SET name = $2;

ba93606a72d667ea81e58c32b541e383c7f24aa4.query:
SELECT l.public_id, l.name, u.public_id host_public_id
            FROM lobby l
                     JOIN lobby_member lm ON l.id = lm.lobby_id
                     JOIN "user" u ON u.id = lm.user_id
            WHERE l.public_id = $1
              AND lm.host IS TRUE;

ce0f7b0a8d2749eeefb3456b28181a642fd8aafa.query:
SELECT l.id, l.public_id, l.name, u.public_id host_public_id
            FROM lobby l
                     JOIN lobby_member lm ON l.id = lm.lobby_id
                     JOIN "user" u ON u.id = lm.user_id
            WHERE l.id > $1
              AND lm.host IS TRUE
            ORDER BY l.id
            LIMIT $2;

dabc471a760fcd9bc5dd348cc87bea7ab957173c.query:
SELECT u.public_id
            FROM "user" u
                     JOIN local l ON u.id = l.user_id
            WHERE l.public_id = $1;

fcca5343de2750cff69730355994397f7d9d235a.query:
INSERT INTO lobby_member (lobby_id, user_id, host)
            VALUES ((SELECT id FROM lobby WHERE public_id = $1),
                    (SELECT id FROM "user" WHERE public_id = $2),
                    $3);
